items.name: INFO
desc: Some information for the client/user (which will typically lead to the selection of an com.sun.star.task.XInteractionApprove continuation).

items.name: QUERY
desc: A query for the client/user (which will typically lead to the selection of an com.sun.star.task.XInteractionApprove or com.sun.star.task.XInteractionDisapprove continuation).

items.name: WARNING
desc: A warning, less severe than an error.
